{
  "ID": "TWITCH_FIREW08E",
  "Name": {
    "English": "TITAN FIREWORK PACK",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "泰坦烟花包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "泰坦煙火包"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Titan Firework Pack",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "泰坦烟花包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "泰坦煙火包"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Pyrotechnics Multi-Pack",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "烟火技术组合包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "煙火表演組合包"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A three-variety pack of luxury fireworks, inspired by the titanic sandworms that stalk the universe. Rich in <span class=\"name name-fuel\">cadmium</span>, <span class=\"name name-commodity\">sodium</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">emeril</span>. Ignite to create glittering displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一包包含三种烟花的奢华烟花包，灵感源自潜伏于宇宙各地的泰坦蠕虫。内含大量的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">钠</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">艾梅里尔</span>。点燃就可以在天空中开启一场炫丽的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "三種豪華煙火的組合包，靈感來自潛伏在宇宙各處的巨大沙蟲，富含<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">鈉</span>與<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>。點燃即可在天空中創造出絢爛效果。<br><br>可從<VAL_ON>建造選單<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>) 放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
